    "title": "SeaKing Leaning Post White Fiberglass Fillet Table (L27.6\" x W11.0\")",
    "body_html": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Free Shipping in Australia</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Leaning Post Top SKL-11</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Built for the dedicated offshore game fisherman, the Leaning Post Top SKL-11 is engineered to </span><span>withstand the toughest conditions. This heavy-duty leaning post features an aluminum plate </span><span>fiberglassed in for secure post mounting, providing the stability and peace of mind needed when </span><span>battling large pelagic fish in challenging offshore environments. Handcrafted with premium composite </span><span>materials, it is designed to meet the rigorous demands of serious game fishing.</span><strong></strong></p>\n<p class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"> </p>",
